title: Diamond 5 - Mid lane looking for DuoQ Jungler
body:
yo I am currently Diamond 5 maining mid lane but can play top decently but it is hard to find a non-flaming Jungler who knows what to do (macro game wise) and since i am lacking macro game knowledge (in exchange for being good micro game wise) i need someone who plays consistent without tiliting or raging who could achieve an early lead for me and the team. hit me up if you are interested.
IGN - kıłłuå (just copy paste it or tell me to add you)

I DO NOT LOOK FOR A CLAN OR ANYTHING PLEASE DON'T WASTE YOU TIME ASKING ME FOR THAT
thanks a lot
have a great day everyone, cya on the rift
